"Owww" Motormaster screams in agony, but grits his teeth, desperate to hold
on to his opponent, he tries to wrap his other hand around, as his first
squeezes, "Now Maximal," he gasps between pained breath "I will crush you
with, uhhhhh ,uhh my bare hands" he shouts.
